Jhasan's decision:

Dr. Dankarrao Chavan Government Medical College, Vishnupuri, Nanded, an institution under the Department, is granted administrative sanction for the purchase of Turnkey Machinery and Equipment at a total cost of Rs. 39,65,00, 000 / - (Rupees Forty-nine Crores, Sixty-five Lakhs only) (inclusive of all taxes) for the treatment of patients admitted to the Osteoarthritis Department of the Institute from the grants sanctioned under the State Plan during the financial year 2024-25 subject to the following conditions under this Government Decision.
